OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FWords by ITV Weather Producer Jennifer
OL,7,FMawby
OL,9,FThis winter, the weather has felt
OL,10,Frelentless.
OL,12,FOver the past three months, the UK has
OL,13,Fbeen battered by four storms and
OL,14,Fconstant weather warnings, bringing a
OL,15,Ftriple threat of wind, rain and snow.
OL,17,FBut has it been the wettest winter on
OL,18,Frecord, and is it usually sunnier?
OL,20,FThe season is not over yet, but here's
OL,21,Fwhat we know so far.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
