OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FA wetter winter for some
OL,8,FYou would be silly not to have carried
OL,9,Fan umbrella this winter, as it felt
OL,10,Flike there was constant rain in many
OL,11,Fparts of the UK.
OL,13,FSo far, England has had 35% more
OL,14,Frainfall than usual, but no records
OL,15,Fhave been broken yet.
OL,17,FHowever, the story is a lot more
OL,18,Finteresting once you look at regional
OL,19,Ffigures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
