OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772197440
OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FScotland experienced 16% less rainfall
OL,7,Fthan it usually would and there was a
OL,8,Fhuge contrast in wet weather depending
OL,9,Fon the region.
OL,11,FWhile eastern parts had 19% more
OL,12,Frainfall than average, northern areas
OL,13,Fsaw a third less rainfall than they
OL,14,Fusually would for this season.
OL,16,FFor the southwest, the figures were a
OL,17,Flot more significant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
