OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FDorset and Cornwall have so far
OL,7,Frecorded their second wettest winter
OL,8,Fon record, and for the Isle of Wight
OL,9,Fand County Down, this was their third
OL,10,Fwettest winter.
OL,12,FCardinham in Cornwall recorded more
OL,13,Fthan 50 days of solid rain; it really
OL,14,Fdidn't ease up.
OL,16,FWhat caused all this rain?
OL,18,FYou might remember the snowstorm in
OL,19,FNorth America in January.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
