OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FAll that cold Arctic air contrasted
OL,7,Fwith the warmer air in the south and
OL,8,Fgave the jet stream more energy and
OL,9,Fpower.
OL,11,FFlights between the US and UK were up
OL,12,Fto 30mph faster than usual thanks to
OL,13,Fthat energised jet stream.
OL,15,FMet Office Senior Scientist Mike
OL,16,FKendon said: "A near-continuous run of
OL,17,FAtlantic systems over the past three
OL,18,Fmonths has brought persistent rain,
OL,19,Fdamaging storms and few dry spells."
