OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FLike a conveyor belt, it brought more
OL,7,Funsettled weather to the UK and was
OL,8,Fthen met with a block of high pressure
OL,9,Fover northern Europe, causing the bad
OL,10,Fweather to stay with us for a longer
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FStorms Bram, Goretti, Ingrid and
OL,14,FChandra brought widespread disruption
OL,15,Ffrom flooding, snow, wind and ice.
OL,17,FDuring Storm Goretti, the Isles of
OL,18,FScilly recorded 99mph wind speeds, the
OL,19,Fhighest recorded for 47 years. Parts
OL,20,Fof the southwest were completely
OL,21,Fflooded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
