OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FProfessor Hannah Cloke, a hydrologist
OL,7,Fat the University of Reading, said:
OL,8,F"It's not just the amount of rain that
OL,9,Fwe've seen that is of issue. It's this
OL,10,Frepeated clustering of rainfall from
OL,11,Fthese different weather systems."
OL,13,FWhy was the southwest so badly hit?
OL,15,FThe jet stream was positioned more
OL,16,Fsouthwards than usual, targeting areas
OL,17,Fsuch as Wales and the south of
OL,18,FEngland, but avoiding the northern
OL,19,Fparts of Scotland.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
