PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772197440
OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FWhat about sunshine?
OL,8,FSo not only has it been wet and
OL,9,Fstormy, but grey too.
OL,11,FSunshine has been below average for
OL,12,Fthe UK, and so far in February, we've
OL,13,Fonly seen about half the amount we
OL,14,Fusually would.
OL,16,FScotland has had its fifth dullest
OL,17,Fwinter since 1910.
OL,19,FTemperatures have, however, been
OL,20,Fhigher than normal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
