OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772197440
OL,3,CHas this been the UK's wettest winter?
OL,4,CWhat the data shows
OL,6,FWe caught a brief glimmer of spring
OL,7,Fsunshine on Wednesday when some areas
OL,8,Frecorded more than 18C.
OL,10,FHow are the final days of winter
OL,11,Flooking?
OL,13,FSadly, there are more showers to come
OL,14,Fthis weekend, but we've got some sunny
OL,15,Fspells to look forward to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
